PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of the following persons as members of the Pacific Pilotage Authority to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years. (ANDREW ALLAN FLOTRE, Victoria, British Columbia, in the place of John McNeill Unwin, whose term has expired; and KIM CHRISTENSEN, Langley, British Columbia, in the place of Alan D. Grimston, whose term has expired)
